<span id="freeTextContainer13192370803854356586"><strong>More than a romance</strong><br/><br/>A powerful story, woven in delicate detail, Grace and Alex don&apos;t disappoint. From the moment he saved her life as a child, this tale draws them together. Very good story. Well done.</span>
  <span id="freeText13192370803854356586" style="display:none"><strong>More than a romance</strong><br /><br />A powerful story, woven in delicate detail, Grace and Alex don't disappoint. From the moment he saved her life as a child, this tale draws them together. Very good story. Well done.</span>
