              <span id="reviewTextContainer557994836" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17172333167135676296">An eclectic book that drags the reader into the story like quicksand. Before you know it, you are deeply threaded into the pages of a suspense romance </span>

          </span>
        </div>


